<title>BCM_GETFILEINFO</title>
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">

<p><font color="#000000" size="4"><strong>BCM_GETFILEINFO</strong></font></p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="3" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td width="100%" bgcolor="#E6E6E6"><pre>BCM_GETFILEINFO
	wParam = 0;
	lParam = ( LPARAM )( LPFILEINFO )lpFileInfo;</pre>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>

<p>Query for file information on the current control contents.</p>

<ul>
    <li>Returns non-zero for success and zero for failure.</li>
</ul>

<dl>
    <dt><em>lpFileInfo</em></dt>
    <dd>A pointer to a <a href="fileinfo.htm">FILEINFO</a> structure which will contain the file information
    on the control contents when the message succeeded.</dd>
</dl>

</body>
</html>